---
title: Chorizo Burrito Bowl with Garlic Rice, Charred Corn Salsa & Sour Cream
description: This burrito bowl is guaranteed to be a new favourite. Our star Tex-Mex spice blend gives the mild chorizo oodles of flavour,  while the charred corn salsa, tangy sour cream and fresh squeeze of lime ties it all together.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chorizo-burrito-bowl-dc509c03.jpg
